Distribution . This species is known from Argentina and Bolivia (
Knight & Stone 1977
). In Argentina , it is known from the following provinces: Chaco, Corrientes, Formosa , Jujuy, Salta, Santa Fe and Santiago del Estero (
Mitchell & Darsie 1985
;
Campos & Maciá 1998
;
Ludueña Almeida et al. 2004
).
